{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"49421-hashim-saves-the-mangoes","title":"Hashim Saves the Mangoes","description":"It is summer and Hashim wants to eat lots of mangoes. But they are getting spoilt. What can he do?\r\n","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ipsita Dasgupta","Rukmini  Das"],"illustrators":["Ananya Broker Parekh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/49421-hashim-saves-the-mangoes"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/717387/size3/a653f7c1c772174401a200560cd41303.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/717387/size6/a653f7c1c772174401a200560cd41303.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87623/size6/fe12a6de9b89629ccadd4412d86e93ce.jpg","text":"2/11","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90939/size6/2f32df05b69e8795f4db19a0c5fab8a1.jpg","text":"Hashim loves mangoes.\nThis summer, the mangoes are about to spoil. \nHashim wants to save them.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87625/size6/76e6c046c77add2ade7d333c284ceb4b.jpg","text":"Baba tells Hashim that if he removes water from \nthe mangoes, they will not spoil.\n“Germs cannot live without water,” he says.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87626/size6/d2f621113834020aa283ff6211692697.jpg","text":"“How do we take water out of the mangoes?” asks Hashim.\n“Add salt to them!” says Baba.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87857/size6/0fa5256cc0e09d62705c9b4cc4dd77c9.jpg","text":"Then Baba and Hashim keep the mangoes out in the sun to dry.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87628/size6/a08ec4a43012b726210db1f539a27831.jpg","text":"They put the mangoes in a bottle with some oil.\nOil doesn’t let germs from the air reach the mangoes.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87858/size6/17958c92defe5aa12e6d8131d7edd97e.jpg","text":"“Baba, we have made pickle!” says Hashim.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87896/size6/01b63f0c93b02c1bd7921be13bd80a5f.jpg","text":"How can we preserve our favourite \nfruits and vegetables?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87631/size6/4402d40f235f077a5ae32c58e937c84e.jpg","text":"Potato slice + boil + dry = potato chips \n(to be fried and eaten)\nAny fruit + sugar + lemon + cook = jam","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/87632/size6/55f35ca72646de1b64cd73db6dd5f61c.jpg","text":"Tomato + salt + sun + oil = sun-dried tomatoes\nLemon + salt = lemon preserves","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":10,"words":145}}